data.name: BigWigs Encounter Tools
data.summary: Modular and lightweight approach to providing you with the tools you need to beat any boss encounter. The efficiently coded alternative to Deadly Boss Mods (DBM) for spell & ability timers.

data.name: Masque
data.summary: A skinning engine for button-based add-ons.

data.name: AtlasLootClassic
data.summary: Shows the possible loot from the bosses

data.name: BigWigs Voice (Korean)
data.summary: A plugin for BigWigs that will play Text-To-Speech sounds for boss abilities in Korean.

data.name: Toggle Chat Visibility
data.summary: A simple addon that allows you to toggle the visibility of chat windows using a keybinding or slash commands.
